-- NYC Pension Chief Schloss Says `8% Return Is Possible' (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-06-06T13:46:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-06/nyc-pension-chief-schloss-says-8-return-is-possible-audio-.html
Lawrence Schloss, New York City's 
chief investment officer and deputy comptroller for pensions, 
says 8 percent return is possible for pension plan holders. 
Schloss talks with Bloomberg's  Tom Keene  and Sara Eisen on 
Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg Surveillance." Guest Host Meredith 
Whitney, analyst and chief executive officer of Meredith Whitney
Advisory Group also joins the discussion.       
(Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 06:09
 